                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The main query combines the results from the account data and manual billing data subqueries using a left join, and orders the final result set by "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
